article.description: Jayden Gardner had 18 points as East Carolina topped Charlotte 66-57 on Friday in the season-opener for both teams.
article.headline: Gardner lifts East Carolina over Charlotte 66-57
article.linkText: Gardner lifts East Carolina over Charlotte 66-57
article.story: Jayden Gardner had 18 points as East Carolina topped Charlotte 66-57 on Friday in the season-opener for both teams. Tristen Newton had 15 points and six rebounds for East Carolina. Jordan Shepherd had 15 points for the 49ers. Jhery Matos added 14 points and Jahmir Young had 10. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
